data.description: Very well maintained 4-bedroom 3 bath home located between Bartow and Eagle Lake.  Open floor plan in living areas with split bedrooms.   Solid wood cabinets with an artist's touch. Solid surface countertops, range, convection/microwave built in, dishwasher, refrigerator.  A well-proportioned walk-in pantry.  Back yard is privacy fenced and offers a unique patio with a gazabo that has electricity, ceiling fan, and grill.
